casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Shayla Deneice TUCKER, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157645
COA: 335393 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 5, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 13, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
